==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hotchkiss gun
<hw>Hotch"kiss gun</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <ety>[After <person>Benjamin B.
<etsep>Hotchkiss</etsep></person> (1826-85), American inventor.]</ety>
<def>A built-up, rifled, rapid-fire gun of oil-tempered steel, having a
rectangular breechblock which moves horizontally or vertically in a
mortise cut completely through the jacket. It is made in
France.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

